data.description: OWNER OFFERING $10,000 TOWARD BUYER CONCESSIONS!! Beautiful 2 year old Rock and Stone Bloomfield home in Star Ranch, Hawthorne Model with loads of extra's! Open concept offers plenty of living space. Upgrades throughout! Kitchen features Under Cabinet lighting, Pot Filler, Granite tops, large walk-in pantry, custom buffet, Gas Cook top and is open to the breakfast room and family room. Loads of windows with faux wood blinds in all rooms. Bedrooms feature built in cubbies and large windows. Primary bedroom features special lighting in bay window area with ensuite bathroom with jetted tub and seperate shower with rainwater shower head. Upstairs bedroom, full bathroom and media-game room. Tankless Water Heater is gas and there is an extra electric water heater, as well! Cat 6 wiring for all your media needs. Sink on patio with gas stub out and sink plumbed in garage. Extra insulation pkg. Home is around the corner from the elementary and 6th grade schools. New High school and stadium!
